## User Flows (New)

```
Flow 1 — Select Curriculum
  User visits /courses
  → Multi-select curriculum cards (qualification + exam board badges)
  → Selections saved to localStorage + LessonContext

Flow 2 — Select Subjects
  (Wizard Step 2 — only shows subjects belonging to selected curricula)
  → Multi-select subjects with "Select All" per curriculum
  → On confirm: INSERT into user_enrollments for each new subject

Flow 3 — Exam Countdown (Auto)
  After each new enrollment:
  → Query: SELECT * FROM exams WHERE subject_id = ? AND date > NOW()
           ORDER BY date ASC LIMIT 1
  → Match found: INSERT into exam_countdowns with that exam's date
  → No match: Show placeholder "Timetable not released yet"
  → Session switcher: user can pull later sessions from the same subject

Flow 4 — Lesson Tracker (Connected)
  /lessons reads from LessonContext (enrolled subjects from user_enrollments)
  → Multi-subject filter bar at top (chip toggles, localStorage-persisted)
  → Only shows subjects the user selected in Course Manager

Flow 5a — Notes (Official tab filter)
  /my-notes → Official tab
  → Toggle: "Filter by my courses"
  → When on: filters notes where curriculum_id ∈ enrolledCurriculumIds
                               OR subject_id   ∈ enrolledSubjectIds
  → Zero new Supabase queries — uses LessonContext enrolled IDs

Flow 5b — Flashcards (Course-aware)
  /flashcards reads decks from Supabase (migrated from mock)
  → Toggle: "My Courses Only"
  → When on: filters decks by curriculum_id / subject_id from LessonContext
  → Create Deck modal pre-fills curriculum/subject from enrolled courses
```

