## Architecture

```
LessonContext (extended — single source of truth)
├── enrolledCurriculums[]          ← from user_enrollments JOIN curriculums/subjects/topics
├── enrolledCurriculumIds[]        ← derived
├── enrolledSubjectIds[]           ← derived
├── selectedCurriculumIds[]        ← user filter, persisted to localStorage
├── selectedSubjectIds[]           ← user filter, persisted to localStorage
├── setSelectedCurriculumIds()
├── setSelectedSubjectIds()
├── countdowns[]                   ← auto-derived: next exam per enrolled subject
├── countdownsLoading
├── progressRecords[]              ← topic_progress
└── updateProgress()

Consumers (all read from one context, zero duplicate fetches):
├── /courses          — Course Manager page (new dashboard)
├── /lessons          — Lesson Tracker (subject filter bar)
├── /countdown        — Auto + Custom countdown sections
├── /my-notes         — Official notes course filter toggle
└── /flashcards       — Supabase decks + course filter
```

